{"tid":42034,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼] 熱狗的四方西邏輯","createTime":"2016-12-16T10:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T23:13:35.000Z","uid":319,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f805a52fe786fac942c3f8f98d29200ed851f817","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"【熱狗邏輯】<br />\n<br />\n1.熱狗曾經幫過你：<br />\n你呢世都要做佢扯線公仔受佢指揮，否則就係叛徒反骨仔<br />\n<br />\n2.你曾經幫過熱狗：<br />\n你要永遠繼續幫佢，否則嗰次幫熱狗就係抽熱狗水。而且今世人永遠只能幫熱狗，不准幫其他人<br />\n<br />\n3.你曾經幫過熱狗，萬一亦幫過其他人：<br />\n兩頭蛇 / 左右逢源 / 牆頭草<br />\n<br />\n4.你從來未幫過熱狗：<br />\n扮瞓死港豬（反而罪名最輕）<br />\n<br />\n5.你唔聲援熱狗：<br />\n你係私怨撚 / 選擇性失明<br />\n<br />\n6.你聲援熱狗：<br />\n貓哭老鼠 / 華麗轉身 / 黐熱狗光環(乜有嘅咩) / 想靠攏熱狗(照下鏡吖唔該)<br />\n<br />\n結論：知唔知咩叫「四方西」呀？即係乜撚都唔啱囉。<br />\n<br />\n#丁蟹量產型<br />\n#做人最緊要正常<br />\n#正直由呢亭人講出嚟難聽過粗口<br />\n#歡迎cap圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/samwongyt/posts/10154785238034402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsamwongyt%2Fposts%2F10154785238034402&d=pV8d1d37%2BPc5ZieEQmfScQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2ff5b893\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/samwongyt/posts/10154785238034402</a>"},{"pid":"5bbefe340c91bc4127dfdba1b1f9f5e575336bc6","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512b247213ff4ff95e5b82f3af67046d26aad034","tid":42034,"uid":62533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nadmin幾時做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cedc023f707163387062a5cb485515f2cd65b3","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img sr