係咩台先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎蒞臨私怨臺 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如直接改名做青症台啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪唔批評得熱狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52bf339a2b5a3b8c760cace935377d5564210cd","tid":42034,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以加多項：<br />\n<br />\n就算果個人係選舉投過票俾熱血公民，但都資格批評熱血公民。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 我對冇投票俾民主黨，但又成日批評佢，表示羞恥！"},{"pid":"13083207f8ffa4bdbf4cdd278c22934f3cc4036b","tid":42034,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以加多項：<br />\n<br />\n就算果個人係選舉投過票俾熱血公民，但都冇資格批評熱血公民。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 我對冇投票俾民主黨，但又成日批評佢，表示羞恥！"},{"pid":"e3b45dd1fa06d2f04b29462e1dcca7f68d404f0b","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我可唔可以加多項：<br />\n<br />\n就算果個人係選舉投過票俾熱血公民，但都資格批評熱血公民。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 我對冇投票俾民主黨，但又成日批評佢，表示羞恥！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係投過票 但無全力叫身邊所有人投<br />\n都無資格批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ab7c695fb48cea4ae04faaff286b0fafaba712","tid":42034,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:50:52.000Z","msg":"最正係第五點"},{"pid":"2b976d94816576ccd9fb4c230c95d356824099cf","tid":42034,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nadmin幾時做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何謂食熱狗？"},{"pid":"dcd2f9ff3fb3caa8bdf4dc03439fb1102715bc2a","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nadmin幾時做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何謂食熱狗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發表任何唔支持/批評熱狗既野就係本民青食熱狗 (好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d04067534d75de8bbd1d2ec83c085c016600c5a","tid":42034,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nadmin幾時做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何謂食熱狗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發表任何唔支持/批評熱狗既野就係本民青食熱狗 (好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有乜問題？有錯就屌，熱狗咩咁巴閉唔屌得？"},{"pid":"38d354a85062a1d0a5c6289b2696488562d0e436","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n何謂食熱狗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發表任何唔支持/批評熱狗既野就係本民青食熱狗 (好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有乜問題？有錯就屌，熱狗咩咁巴閉唔屌得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知 因為我都係佢地所謂「青症食熱狗」既大軍一分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f482938b56634d039f02f44454151e16d03634","tid":42034,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"其實冇幫過熱狗唔係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\n係選舉論壇上直接攻擊熱普城既先係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\nck<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ccbc491ae94c9d03bdef1d5fd077c214053288","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實冇幫過熱狗唔係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\n係選舉論壇上直接攻擊熱普城既先係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\nck<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec74ca3ee1212a86b724f8c8abacf6dcc0247a87","tid":42034,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實冇幫過熱狗唔係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\n係選舉論壇上直接攻擊熱普城既先係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\nck<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚大隻 點蝦得落啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b06e4c68bc1129f1c714d708e14856952eca7b","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實冇幫過熱狗唔係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\n係選舉論壇上直接攻擊熱普城既先係最低罪名<br />\n<br />\nck<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚大隻 點蝦得落啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d70f0dec2ad08516ef353635ea29bde896f9268","tid":42034,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nadmin幾時做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何謂食熱狗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發表任何唔支持/批評熱狗既野就係本民青食熱狗 (好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有乜問題？有錯就屌，熱狗咩咁巴閉唔屌得？</blockquote><br />\n拿屌熱狗就無問題既<br />\n係唔好五十步笑百步啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多野熱狗已經柒左一次 前車可鑑 希望後世唔好犯同樣既錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149142ee5bc5a71ec535dad54a8f2864f1a2c043","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發表任何唔支持/批評熱狗既野就係本民青食熱狗 (好似係)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有乜問題？有錯就屌，熱狗咩咁巴閉唔屌得？</blockquote><br />\n拿屌熱狗就無問題既<br />\n係唔好五十步笑百步啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多野熱狗已經柒左一次 前車可鑑 希望後世唔好犯同樣既錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解屌熱狗就係五十步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌之前要申報自己唔係本民青支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a83daf5a7e5bb19ce7961f53b20bed18d5f832c","tid":42034,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 而家連登都有青症食熱狗大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nadmin幾時做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇下呢個係咩台先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎蒞臨私怨臺 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如直接改名做青症台啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢兩隻熱狗真係唔話得~<br />\n完美示範四方西論第五點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09de6ca5adf27971b3dce0aa7e57da4fd918d30","tid":42034,"uid":47432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"熱狗近排靜靜地又有青狗出黎挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b701544fbd443048a0e28821e5f88786791579f","tid":42034,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗近排靜靜地又有青狗出黎挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31504189ac9974f7fc89601fb1e0c0ee38b3e91","tid":42034,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"10/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}